\c 150
\s Rumbidzai Jehovha!
\p
\v 1 Rumbidzai Jehovha! Rumbidzai Mwari panzvimbo yake tsvene; murumbidzei muchadenga chesimba rake.
\v 2 Murumbidzei nekuda kwezviito zvake zvine simba; murumbidzei zvinoenderana neuwandu hweukuru hwake.
\v 3 Murumbidzei nekuridzwa kwehwamanda; murumbidzei nemitengeranwa nembira.
\v 4 Murumbidzei nengoma nekutamba; murumbidzei nezviridzwa zvine hungiso nenyere.
\v 5 Murumbidzei nemakandira anorira; murumbidzei nemakandira anorira zvikuru.
\v 6 Chose chine mweya wekufema ngachirumbidze Jehovha. Rumbidzai Jehovha!